<head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><base href="&mvte:global:basehref;"><title>Authorized Sinister Diesel Resellers</title><meta name="description" content="Learn why purchasing Sinister Diesel products from an authorized dealer protects product authenticity, warranty eligibility and support access."><mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1"><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" /><mvt:else><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" /></mvt:if><mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" /></head>
<body class="single-column sd2-policy-page"><mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" /><mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />
<main class="sd2-cp sd2-policy"><section class="sd2-policy__hero"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><nav class="sd2-policy__breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="&mvte:urls:SFNT:auto;">Home</a><span>/</span><span>Authorized resellers</span></nav><p class="sd2-cp__eyebrow">Authenticity / Buyer protection</p><h1>Know who<br>you buy from.</h1><p>Authorized channels protect product authenticity, warranty eligibility and access to current Sinister Diesel support.</p><div class="sd2-cp__actions"><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--primary" href="dealer-application.html">Become a dealer</a><a class="sd2-cp__button" href="identifying-genuine-sinister-parts.html">Identify genuine parts</a></div></div></section>
	<div class="sd2-cp__signal"><div><span>01</span><strong>Authentic product</strong></div><div><span>02</span><strong>Eligible coverage</strong></div><div><span>03</span><strong>Supported purchase</strong></div></div>
	<section class="sd2-cp__section"><div class="sd2-cp__shell sd2-policy__layout"><aside><p class="sd2-cp__label">Authorized channel</p><h2>Protect the full ownership experience.</h2><p>Price is only one part of the purchase. Authenticity, complete components and a traceable seller matter when support is needed.</p><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--primary" href="help-center.html">Ask for help</a></aside><article class="sd2-policy__content"><mvt:item name="readytheme" param="contentsection( 'authorized-resellers' )" /></article></div></section>
</main><mvt:item name="hdft" param="footer" /><mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_footer" /></body></html>
